<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Stadium seats.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Inscribed on the seats. Row J: on seats at west end. Row V: cut on the front rim of one seat. Row W: on the front rims of seats, starting on second from west end. Row X: on the front rims of seats, starting at west end. </p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Row J: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.13</measure>. Row V: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.07</measure>. Row W: carefully cut, standard forms with seriphs; <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.08</measure>. Row X: well-cut, cursive; <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.06</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0600" exact="none">Second to sixth centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">context</rs>)
</p>
</div>
